high_descs: Turn right, head to the tub, turn left to face the tub.
Pick up the sponge in the tub.
Turn around, bring the sponge to the sink.
Clean the sponge in the sink with water.
Turn right with the sponge, bring the sponge over to the white shelves on the wall.
Put the sponge on the top shelf to the left.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned sponge on a top shelf.

high_descs: Turn to your right move forward and face the tub on you left
Pick up the sponge on the tub
Turn to your left and go to the sink
Put the sponge in the sink and rinse it
Turn right then head to the shelf rack on your right
Put the sponge on the very top of the shelf rack beside the blue bottle
anns.task_desc: Put a clean sponge on the shelf rack

turn around and head to the sink
wet tie sponge in the sink
